If we configure Issue Creation via email and use the option *CC Watchers* to add CC'ed emails as watchers of the issue, the CC'ed emails are actually added as watchers (if the issue is created successfully), but *they aren't notified of the creation of the issue*. Only when another event is triggered then will they receive a notification.

The diagnosis is the notification event is fired before the CC'ed emails are added as watchers. This is not an expected behavior as customers would like the CC'ed Watchers to be notified of the creation of the issue.

